hjb.http.cmd
Interface JMSCommandGenerator

All Known Implementing Classes:
PatternMatchingCommandGenerator
public interface JMSCommandGenerator

JMSCommandGenerator declares methods used to handle the generation and usage of JMSCommand for a given request.

Author:
Tim Emiola

                throws HJBException
